	(text_box "To program the device, connect a TC2050-NL cable from the device to a ARM SWD adapter.\n\nUSB_DET provides a signal for the microcontroller to know if the device is powered by the USB.\n\nThe reset switch button can be pressed to reset the device in case it gets irrecoverably stuck."
